{"tid":1241390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"做文宣係要分化對家，但前線警渣唔係無辜㗎！","createTime":"2019-06-18T16:33:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T17:29:20.000Z","uid":207710,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd90fbcf1763c28b6da916129fc7769eb3b3838","tid":1241390,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪做文宣做到上腦<br />\n要提吓大家<br />\n上頭落咩order都好<br />\n前線警渣係落手打鳩人嗰個<br />\n仲要唔係普通咁打<br />\n係往死裡打<br />\n好多扮廢老嘅，已經不知不覺間同情緊前線警渣<br />\n分化人結果令自己立場轉埋<br />\n有呢個感覺嘅朋友真係要唞唞<br />\n616佢派啲女警少裝備喺前線就係想你哋以為唔關前線事<br />\n淨係後面落order嘅要負責<br />\n風向少少轉緊，小心！"},{"pid":"63ed35301f5596b76fe850decd658ed11dc7cac8","tid":1241390,"uid":207710,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"「前線警渣只係畀上頭出賣」呢個論調只係氹廢老<br />\n唔係事實！！！"},{"pid":"7d88c1101b176e5309b88294bae4860ee39d4175","tid":1241390,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"657347023e2f5ea8ad94c2515854c3356b250dbf","tid":1241390,"uid":207710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:36:45.000Z","msg":"見到嗰種「警察都有好人」嘅論調重現好驚<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正義嘅警察五年前已經無晒</span></span>"},{"pid":"9f71711de7accf5a94451b0336a043c00d962878","tid":1241390,"uid":207710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:38:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c261e1a8f10452a595ce8a6600e8a8b0423ad4a8","tid":1241390,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7c30e45c821566f872cb938a13bad15f97015a7","tid":1241390,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d529e9ea9accf241de2127848a02cf2505aa93e9","tid":1241390,"uid":258550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:42:33.000Z","msg":"借位宣傳吓 ～裡面有齊各投訴警察部門聯絡及 Template 信 <br />\n【集合】投訴